divs: Sighting Detailswhile out walking my dog at 7 pm i noticed a orb like ball of light traveling from the west going east. This event took place just above the George Washington bridge leading from ny to nj. The amazing thing was just after the 1st appeared, a 2nd ball of light tailed it from behind a short distance. There was no shape but 2 balls of light. They were completely silent. there are constant planes flying above with 3 major airports in the area. These were not planes , helicopters or blimps.
